{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "第六回\"飞来艳福\"承接前文，燕十三与乌鸦在山坡上讨论曹冰暗中偷学三少爷剑法之事。燕十三判断曹冰下一个目标必是谢晓峰，决定即刻赶赴神剑山庄。乌鸦虽受伤仍坚持留下，二人依依惜别之际，一辆快马轻车忽然出现。燕十三犹豫是否要抢劫路人，马车却自动停下，一个嘶哑声音邀他上车。车厢中的黑衣人以酒相待，言语间透露女子身份，声音由嘶哑转为娇美动听。黑衣人突然脱去衣衫，赫然是夏侯世家大少奶奶薛可人。燕十三大惊失色，薛可人却若无其事地靠近他，坦言对丈夫夏侯星的极度不满，称其\"比猪还懒，比木头还不解温柔，比狗还会咬人\"，三年来日夜盼望着逃离。本章通过燕十三与薛可人的机智对话，展现了古龙式的幽默与悬念，为后续故事埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，他用的就是这一招！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你怎么知道是这一招？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "因为他只有用这一招才能击败你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "这绝不是点苍剑法，也绝不是你的剑法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "当然不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "这一招是谁的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "你应该猜得出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "这就是三少爷的剑法？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "除了他还有谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "至少还有你，还有曹冰！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你要去神剑山庄就快去，我留下。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "可是你已受了伤，一个人留在这里……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你放心，我死不了的，你应该担心的是你自己。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "我自己？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "从这里到绿水湖并不远，这一路上已不会有人再替你付账了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "除非你的运气特别好，很快就能遇见一个骑着快马的有钱人，先抢他的钱，再夺他的马。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "你放心，这种事我并不是做不出的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你快去，只要你不死，我保证你一定还可以再见到我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "我若死了，一定会叫人把我的剑送给你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你是不是说过，一个快死的人，运气总是特别好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "我说过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "看起来你的运气现在好像又要来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我相信这种事你是一定能做得出的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "这种好运气绝不会有第二次的。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "也许我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "急着要赶路的人，就请上车来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "运气特别好的人，也未必真的就快死了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "只要我不死，我保证你也一定会再见到我的，就算你不想再见我都不行。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你能不能尽快载我到翠云峰，绿水湖去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "要不要喝两口？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你是不是人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "是不是活人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到现在为止还是的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "但你却不想知道我是谁。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你也是个人，而且一定也是个活人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "这就够了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很够了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我的马车并不是偷来的，酒也不是偷来的，我为什么要无缘无故的请你上车，送你到绿水湖，而且还请你喝酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你高兴！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你不想看看我是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不想！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我不想惹麻烦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你知道我有麻烦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个无缘无故就请人坐车喝酒的人，多多少少总有点毛病。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "是有毛病？还是有麻烦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个有毛病的人，多多少少总会有点麻烦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "也许你看过我之后，就会觉得纵然为我惹点麻烦，也是值得的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "因为我是个女人，而且很好看。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "一个很好看的女人，总希望让别人看看她的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "别人若是拒绝了她，她就一定会觉得是种侮辱，一定会伤心。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "一个女人伤心难受的时候，就往往会做出一些莫名其妙的事！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "譬如说什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "譬如说，她说不定会忽然把自己请来的客人赶下车去！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你为什么不看我？你不敢？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你总算还是个男人，总算还有点胆子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "可是我就算看三天三夜，我也看不出。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "看不出什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "看不出你究竟是不是个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你应该看得出的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "如果我不是人，你看我像什么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "你很像是个女人，可是你做的事却不像！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你想不通我为什么要这样做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "如果我能想得出，我也不是人了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你认为你自己很丑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "还不算太丑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "很老？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "也不算太老。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "有没有什么缺陷？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "没有！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "有没有女人喜欢过你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "有几个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "那么奇怪的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "如果你是别的女人，我非但不会奇怪，而且也不会客气，可惜你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "你有丈夫！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "女人迟早总要嫁人的，嫁了人后，就一定会有丈夫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "如果她嫁的不是个人，她算不算有丈夫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "如果一个女人嫁给了一条猪，一条狗，一块木头，她能不能算有丈夫？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "夏侯星是猪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "不是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "如果他是狗，也许反倒好一点。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "因为狗至少还懂一点人意，有一点人性。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "夏侯星比猪还懒，比木头还不解温柔，比狗还会咬人，却偏偏还要装出一副很了不起的样享，我嫁给他三年，每天都恨不得溜走。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "你为什么不溜？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "因为我从来都没有机会，平时他从来都不许我离开他一步。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    }
